-- Arsenal to Play Milan in Soccer’s Champions League; Chelsea to Meet Napoli
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2011-12-16T11:37:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/arsenal-to-play-milan-chelsea-faces-napoli-in-soccer-s-champions-league.html
Arsenal will play AC Milan in
soccer’s Champions League round of 16, while Chelsea will travel
to Napoli.  Defending champion Barcelona will play Bayern Leverkusen
and Real Madrid is matched up with  CSKA Moscow .  Inter Milan 
plays Marseille and Cyprus’ APOEL will play Lyon. Zenit  St.
Petersburg  takes on Benfica and Basel hosts Bayern Munich.  The two-game round, which matches the runners up of the
group round with winners of that stage, will be played in
February and March. The runners up will host the opening match,
with the higher seeded teams playing the final game at home.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  